sources.description:
Trial By Fire - Kristin Scott was following in her father's footsteps when she became a fire fighter. But she's about to step into uncharted territory as she strives to be the first woman ever accepted into the elite smokejumpers, the most dangerous form of fire fighting. Now, Kristin has four weeks of rookie training to prove that she can do what no woman in her field has done before. When a treacherous wildfire threatens the lives of her family, it will take all of her might and resolve to defeat this disaster and save her loved ones.
2008.  Stars: Brooke Burns, Rick Ravanello, Winston Rekert
